snippet.title: Oscar Experts predictions slugfest: How will 'West Side Story,' 'Nightmare Alley' shake things up?
snippet.description:
Gold Derby editors and Experts Christopher Rosen and Joyce Eng discuss the last two big contenders of the season, Steven Spielberg's remake of "West Side Story" and Guillermo del Toro's first post-"Shape of Water" film, "Nightmare Alley."
